snippet.title: Frank McCaughey
snippet.description:
I do podcasts and make videos. I like to chat with interesting people about lots of different subjects
It's not really interviews as such. I hope for authentic, unedited, unfiltered style banter.
Of late I am doing more video works and started a video diary piece about fitness.
I write here at https://www.unknowing.life
General website www.frankmccaughey.com
